reviews.review_text: Standing In A Shaft Of Light my God! This is an incredible source, like drinking from a running stream in the middle of a massive forest. I can’t believe this exists out there…for free! Thank you so much to aLL parties involved in the construction of this tape. NFA * Nick 3/8/23

Fantastic Wish I had been born a few years earlier,  you can hear the echo of the old garden,  brings back alot of memories. First set is killer and it gets better from there.   Terrapin Samson is short but intense,  and Jerry bangs out US Blues like he's walking distance from Bunker Hill lol.. this show doesn't get enough respect.
